// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2338 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 66284d1b-eb52-5114-9594-83f26ed62a93

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
